<br>
Also... be aware that Dell technical support is only as good as the technician you're talking to. They are not all equal in expertise. Many simply follow the script. If they can't figure it out they tell you to wipe and restore to factory. *shrug*<br>
<br>
as always, your mileage may vary.<br>
